# Workspace Portability Requirements

**Workspace:** [WORKSPACE_NAME]
**Last updated:** [DATE]

This file documents everything needed to reproduce this workspace's working environment on a new machine.

---

## Workspace path

This workspace **must** be cloned to the following exact path:

```
[ABSOLUTE_WORKSPACE_PATH]
```

**Why:** The `skills/` directory contains relative symlinks (`[RELATIVE_SYMLINK_PATH]`). If the workspace is placed at a different path, all symlinks will break and skills will be unavailable.

---

## Required software

| Software | Purpose | Install command |
